CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778263866
OL,3,CReform UK deputy leader at Birmingham
OL,4,Celection count as Labour losses
OL,5,Cexpected
OL,7,FThe Boston and Skegness MP said it was
OL,8,Ftoo early to gauge the extent of his
OL,9,Fparty's success in Birmingham.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV News on his confidence
OL,12,Fat taking Birmingham Tice said,
OL,13,F"there's a long way to go, it's very
OL,14,Ftight, every individual declaration is
OL,15,Ftense, it's exciting, nerve-wracking"
OL,16,Fbut said there is a "turquoise wave
OL,17,Fwhich is cascading through the West
OL,18,FMidlands"
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
