CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1778263866
OL,3,CReform UK deputy leader at Birmingham
OL,4,Celection count as Labour losses
OL,5,Cexpected
OL,7,FHe referred to Reform UK's strong
OL,8,Fshowing in parts of Staffordshire, a
OL,9,Fyear after it won control of the
OL,10,Fcounty council, saying "Voters are
OL,11,Fdoubling down and saying thank you
OL,12,Fvery much Reform councils for what
OL,13,Fyou've done so far."
OL,15,FSince Reform UK took control of
OL,16,FStaffordshire County Council, two
OL,17,Fcouncillors have been forced to resign
OL,18,Fover racism allegations.
OL,26,@rD@XOUuD@TO]
